# SPA fallback — every non-asset path serves index.html so the client
# router can pick up the URL (e.g. /123 → puzzle #123).
#
# Used by Netlify, Cloudflare Pages, and Render. If deploying to Vercel,
# this file is ignored — Vercel uses vercel.json at the repo root instead.
#
# The 200 status (not 301/302) is critical: it serves index.html *at*
# the requested URL without redirecting, so the path stays /123 (which
# is what the JS router reads on boot).

/*    /index.html   200
